Appendix C: FAQs
Q: How quickly can I get a loan?
A: You'll receive eligibility report within 1 hour and sanction within 7 days for most loan types.

Q: What's your fee structure?
A: We work on a commission model paid by lenders. Customers pay only standard processing fees to the lender.

Q: Can you help with low credit scores?
A: Yes, we have partners who specialize in profile-building and work with varied credit profiles.

Q: Do you serve areas outside Madurai?
A: Yes, we serve all Tamil Nadu districts and have successfully processed loans for clients across South India.

